nodes.id: 河南种子案

zh-cn: 河南种子案

description.zh-cn: 2003年5月，洛阳市中级人民法院审理的一起民事案件。审判长李慧娟因认定《河南省农作物种子管理条例》的部分条款抵触《中华人民共和国种子法》而无效，引发了司法与立法的冲突。
description.en: A civil case tried by the Luoyang Intermediate People's Court in May 2003. The presiding judge, Li Huijuan, ruled that some provisions of the 'Henan Provincial Regulations on the Administration of Crop Seeds' were invalid because they conflicted with the 'Seed Law of the People's Republic of China', which triggered a conflict between the judiciary and the legislature.

relationships.source: 中原豫西洛阳市人民法院
relationships.target: 洛阳市人民政府司法科

description.zh-cn: 1949年9月，中原豫西洛阳市人民法院改为洛阳市人民政府司法科。
description.en: In September 1949, the Zhongyuan Yuxi Luoyang Municipal People's Court was changed to the Judicial Section of the Luoyang Municipal People's Government.

relationships.source: 洛阳市人民政府司法科
relationships.target: 河南省洛阳市人民法院

description.zh-cn: 1951年9月《中华人民共和国人民法院暂行组织条例》颁布后，洛阳市人民政府司法科改为河南省洛阳市人民法院。
description.en: After the promulgation of the 'Provisional Regulations on the Organization of People's Courts of the People's Republic of China' in September 1951, the Judicial Section of the Luoyang Municipal People's Government was changed to the Luoyang Municipal People's Court of Henan Province.

relationships.source: 河南省洛阳市人民法院
relationships.target: 河南省洛阳市中级人民法院

description.zh-cn: 1955年9月27日，河南省洛阳市人民法院改为河南省洛阳市中级人民法院。
description.en: On September 27, 1955, the Luoyang Municipal People's Court of Henan Province was changed to the Luoyang Intermediate People's Court of Henan Province.

relationships.source: 王子俊
relationships.target: 中原豫西洛阳市人民法院

description.zh-cn: 王子俊于1948年9月6日就任中原豫西洛阳市人民法院院长。
description.en: Wang Zijun took office as the President of the Zhongyuan Yuxi Luoyang Municipal People's Court on September 6, 1948.

relationships.source: 森蔚
relationships.target: 河南省洛阳市中级人民法院

description.zh-cn: 森蔚于1955年9月27日就任河南省洛阳市中级人民法院院长。
description.en: Sen Wei took office as the President of the Luoyang Intermediate People's Court of Henan Province on September 27, 1955.

relationships.source: 李慧娟 (法官)
relationships.target: 河南省洛阳市中级人民法院

description.zh-cn: 在2003年5月的“河南种子案”中，李慧娟担任河南省洛阳市中级人民法院的审判长。
description.en: In the 'Henan Seed Case' of May 2003, Li Huijuan served as the presiding judge of the Luoyang Intermediate People's Court of Henan Province.

relationships.source: 河南种子案
relationships.target: 河南省农作物种子管理条例

description.zh-cn: 在河南种子案中，审判长李慧娟认定《河南省农作物种子管理条例》的部分条款因抵触《中华人民共和国种子法》而不具备法律效力。
description.en: In the Henan Seed Case, presiding judge Li Huijuan ruled that parts of the 'Henan Provincial Regulations on the Administration of Crop Seeds' were legally invalid because they conflicted with the 'Seed Law of the People's Republic of China'.

relationships.source: 河南省人民代表大会
relationships.target: 李慧娟 (法官)

description.zh-cn: 在“河南种子案”后，李慧娟的判决遭到了河南省人民代表大会的强烈指责。
description.en: After the 'Henan Seed Case', Li Huijuan's verdict was strongly criticized by the Henan Provincial People's Congress.

relationships.source: 河南省洛阳市中级人民法院
relationships.target: 李浩

description.zh-cn: 2012年11月30日，河南省洛阳市中级人民法院对“洛阳性奴案”作出一审宣判，判处被告人李浩死刑。
description.en: On November 30, 2012, the Luoyang Intermediate People's Court of Henan Province delivered a first-instance verdict in the 'Luoyang Sex Slave Case', sentencing the defendant Li Hao to death.

relationships.source: 河南省洛阳市中级人民法院
relationships.target: “殴打20年前班主任”案

description.zh-cn: 2019年8月19日，河南省洛阳市中级人民法院对“殴打20年前班主任”案作出二审判决，维持原判。
description.en: On August 19, 2019, the Luoyang Intermediate People's Court of Henan Province issued a second-instance judgment in the 'Case of Beating a Teacher from 20 Years Ago', upholding the original verdict.
